# Alfresco integration with Cisco Spark

Get ALFRESCO document status change notifications to a SPARK room of your choice

This integration is a way of following the status change of your documents in Alfresco by receiving notifications in your Cisco Spark room.

Status changes you receive notifications for are:

• file created (or moved in)
• file updated
• file deleted (or moved out)

No need to monitor Alfresco or wait for an email notification in your mail client anymore. Receive them right in you Cisco Spark!


# Get Started and Setup

To start download this repository (green button Download). After that follow instructions
from the file "User and install guide".